headline: Short-Term Rentals: Airbnb's Dominance and Booking's Gains in 1 Chart
summary: The big three online travel agencies are generating almost three-quarters of the short-term rental revenue on the planet. The rest of the crowd is seeing their previous foothold diminishing.
